                          "message": "Started task from script: \"option task = {name: \\\"task1\\\", every: 30m} from(bucket: \\\"iot_center\\\") |> range(start: -90d) |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == \\\"environment\\\") |> aggregateWindow(every: 1h, fn: mean)\""
